rows.label: tev910501_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev910501_SEL0020
rows.name: Ask about Grenada Galactic.

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0030
rows.name:
Our corporate philosophy centers around
aiding humanity's survival through the
development of "martial expedients."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0040
rows.name:
That said, some in the company's upper
echelons still put profits first, or are trying
to get a foothold in the government...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0050
rows.name:
We've left Earth behind, but they're still
stuck in the same old mindsets... I wish
there was something I could do about it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_JNK0060
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev910501_SEL0070
rows.name: Ask how she's been doing lately.

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0080
rows.name:
Oh, uh, I'm sorry.
I have to get back to work soon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0090
rows.name:
If you have questions about Grenada GG's
product lineup, you can direct them to the
company's service desk.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_JNK0100
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev910501_SEL0110
rows.name: Ask about Liesel.

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0120
rows.name:
If Liesel offered you her help, no strings
attached, that means she must've really
taken a shine to you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0130
rows.name:
She can be a handful sometimes, but if
she's with you, she's REALLY with you,
if you know what I mean.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0140
rows.name:
I hope you can look after her,
even as she looks after you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_JNK0150
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev910501_SEL0160
rows.name: Ask how she's been doing lately.

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0170
rows.name:
The new Hraesvelg model has been
selling like hotcakes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0180
rows.name:
Thanks to Liesel's prudent testing, even
the frontline pilots are rating it highly.
Seems we're catering to our audience.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0190
rows.name:
Remember—in the weapons industry, you
can't be in it for your own ego. It's all for
the soldiers who'll be using them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0200
rows.name:
I'm hoping that recent events have
reminded our bosses of that, too...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_JNK0210
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev910501_SEL0220
rows.name: Ask about the new company she founded.

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0230
rows.name:
For the time being, it seems my main
activities will be building the business
plan and recruitment.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0240
rows.name:
Hraesvelg's turned a lot of heads,
so it was easy to bring in some sponsors.
That's some silver lining, at least...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0250
rows.name:
We're off to a good start, but I don't
want us to get ahead of ourselves.
We'll ramp up slowly—go at our own pace.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0260
rows.name: ...Liesel and I promised each other that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_JNK0270
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev910501_SEL0280
rows.name: Ask how she's been doing lately.

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0290
rows.name:
After quitting my job at Grenada and
going freelance, I thought I'd feel free,
but honestly, I just feel a bit lost.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0300
rows.name:
I've always worked for big corporations.
This is the first time I'm my own boss.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0310
rows.name:
Don't get me wrong, as an engineer
I'm pretty confident, but as a person,
a member of society... Well, I'll learn.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0320
rows.name: Cancel

rows.label: tev910501_MSG0330
rows.name: Cancel
